  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄 솔루션 전문</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a344772-298b-413d-9b0f-cd020ead39be\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806865943/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">아직 엑셀에 의존하는 인쇄소를 위해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>엑셀</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a57cec74-1276-4799-bc79-31936b65d833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 위대하다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ca843d4-e29a-4f93-b635-15f2f6e69150\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a513b44d-d833-4367-9d88-e8c18bda5b68\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5a8b288b-6006-4d8e-8403-e611e5180345\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-423637f6-68d3-4704-a14d-f8506ec9d176\" style=\"color:#555555;\">어느 현자의 말에 의하면 20세기 가장 위대한 발명 중에 하나가 마이크로소프트의 오피스 프로그램이라고 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-acf006ea-63f3-4dc1-8b2a-5c95e5d0d2a0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-44b73a24-9e95-424d-a3e3-cdc2c719ed32\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92fc859f-aef9-484f-bba9-dfc7a02692c6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-02f997f0-c677-489f-8e76-713c5ab3263d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그중에서도 엑셀은 관리용 프로그램으로서 수십 년 동안 명성을 이어오고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c1416500-24f6-4b94-a834-635cd09fde7c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0508d4f7-06c7-4748-9110-f9b210f4a42b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-975612d6-f9e1-41d8-bbda-576750facfe4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6060a13a-ffdc-4cf7-b82c-cb3bb1188ed3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제가 30년 인쇄인으로 살아오는 동안 내부 매출이나 매입을 아직도 엑셀에 의존해서 관리하는 업체가 어림잡아 거의 70% 이상은 차지하고 있는 것 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea6cc168-e50e-405c-9ac9-2342b1c3f1f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1944a0b2-71d9-4ba3-9862-0bf7d1ffa3d2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b4b24f0-e4d0-450a-8879-dc62f40be62a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-425d7d70-adde-4cfe-a6b3-08da917aa140\" style=\"color:#555555;\">심지어는 내부 인트라넷이 있음에도 불구하고 그 사용성이나 익숙함 때문에 디테일한 관리는 엑셀을 병행하여 사용하는 업체가 많은 것으로 파악됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-099e59f9-7078-432a-9c07-b64c7f2a5a43\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2179d2c2-705a-4a81-bfad-bf7407b671d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-05e3abf6-3ecd-4a63-9427-097c24bab519\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ae327b7-2464-4735-b8f3-30a93420e76a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그래서 2022년 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 약 3개월의 독학으로 인쇄관리용 프로그램을 완성하여 기본 토대를 진행했었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e09c8de5-3907-4554-a585-26d102367d7c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8a780869-5c3c-44a8-8633-6c34de095ea5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4dc42dc2-21a8-4198-a720-352af229d917\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6bd1b699-05e0-4654-8ec3-e8d6e906fdd4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">인쇄 프로세스를 이해하는 전문적인 PM이 있기에 가능했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-abda7d3a-0f7a-4259-bc72-aa93762e6c9c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba65ee1b-53e3-4769-9df0-5807eed0e69f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c59324a-661a-4010-89f0-47e38d4027b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-97160c5c-49fc-487f-af17-8d33d73917a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5a464a91-367f-451e-bc2f-61c8b659395e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c8657ad-8d06-4f48-9ecf-54a8e2b17d40\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4616be0a-f722-4487-8ef3-20e534fa021d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 작업을 시작한 이유는 기본 토대를 만들려고 하는 초석의 문제였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d61c5a3-84b3-42c9-8ce2-8e655672ece2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f93250d3-ca30-4b70-9c21-8910537fb463\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7f73136-4c3e-47d7-8cbc-4b1d7db11d0f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-787a296a-35df-4f97-8e0a-b4cf93c1e0ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d380adcf-8811-4c70-aae0-d769f0f9e055\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1620069f-5787-447e-944c-31c3985408e3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 프로그램이 과연 인쇄인들에게 반응이 있을까를 고민해 봤습니다. 이 과정에서 다음과 같은 의문(?)이 생겨났습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-448747a3-751d-4bb8-90cf-cc7abacaf879\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c09a7f13-552a-45a0-b2f5-93dd309061de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-24668c1a-8285-4f9e-8ed3-641d3ea64603\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-70836fa9-cb02-4688-90ad-8dc92d31125c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>하나, 이 인쇄 영업용 엑셀이 범용적일까?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9169334e-7144-448f-99f2-e81f3d88fc63\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d40bca79-737d-4056-9468-3de17788cd53\" style=\"color:#555555;\">참 애석하게도 이 엑셀이 인쇄인을 위해 만능적으로 사용될 만큼 범용적이지 않습니다. 그리고 각 회사의 특성에 맞는 범용적인 프로그램을 만드는 것은 불가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4b9d2e9-cebb-4f48-938b-9b2275269437\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d90ae895-766c-44db-aeb6-5b5274c2d459\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb88aa90-5160-4502-a2f0-4e72a8d58fa7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8b1200e0-7d77-4919-b677-aed6551e5227\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>하나, 이 엑셀이 완성도가 높을까?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-197646b2-6c3e-4d73-be5f-db2777d49ae4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-407714e7-30b6-4e16-bc80-29f9bedf3e55\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 부분도 70점이라고 말씀드리겠습니다. 저희 자동견적 솔루션을 아시는 분들은 100점짜리 솔루션이라고 설명드리지 않습니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2630cf60-2300-416a-a267-9a94bf4d5b1b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">저희는 70점의 기본 토대 위에 30점을 고객의 사양에 맞춰 개발하는 것을 주 무기로 생각합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3610af60-944c-4537-bc79-97f5e5f8734c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8c694ee9-601e-4d2b-8d7d-667f6512d427\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f68e351-621c-4f9d-9ab3-e1341fa61938\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3775619a-9a47-4d17-87bb-0cc1fb43e37e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">찍어 내기가 아닌 고객 맞춤 개발이 그 본질인 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a175c62c-1dc9-4b57-b5e9-4c2445f6e92d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-994a86a3-c9fb-4fa2-af4f-6a0fb16286ae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-788be865-7086-4456-be59-5bde31d49db8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0dc63227-7e4d-4a07-89aa-a37de24de73f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 엑셀도 동일한 관점에서 제안 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b456215-28b2-4ddd-9368-fe0655589ed0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d37c4dc6-e69f-40fa-92c5-14df2583301c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a7f0b691-a77e-4694-98e1-da68534102ee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f8f7ff19-1d2c-4a7f-8040-5e51e5ad554b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 여러분이 직원 3인 이하의 소규모 인쇄소라면 이 엑셀을 본인 회사에 맞게 맞춤 개발하는 것을 고민해 보십시오.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53faf8a6-798c-47c6-bfaf-34987a3f4cf6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7ba32629-d112-41e1-a040-ad833e3f0be3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e33b6284-54fa-4925-a811-09ecb45374e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-764b7538-bc90-487d-ab09-8c6199bd4239\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 여러분 회사가 사이트 홍보보다는 지인 영업으로 하청을 주로 받는다면 이 엑셀로 개발해서 매입/매출을 산정해 보는 것을 고민해 보십시오.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6f4f5fd5-7000-460e-a0d9-8a3cb92424ad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-11daea76-d591-44a4-81c5-ea0f7420189c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7c625048-8a86-42af-bacc-5fc0714c2fb9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-52c1068d-7905-4deb-af47-6d8dcd470f48\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ca97d22-958e-42cc-a9da-968d834fd457\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a03261be-b85e-47d8-8086-ac270143c300\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 엑셀의 장점은 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b83cd8b6-be00-4d10-9e89-eb389b32ee2f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-28bc87a3-4082-4cb6-98c9-01551a96bbc7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4afb34a5-a5a4-463a-bda1-d520bd00e8b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b3326e19-5135-4248-bec9-4b9c5c4d88e3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 비용이 저렴합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f0d41981-5864-4f4d-a1de-46855a8e1e21\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6eda132-abf3-44a5-b16d-975d5d12c225\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 개발 기간이 비교적 짧습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-340d3a8e-b0af-4b03-9b94-0844963c0ff4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0a434325-3c73-4625-a106-e15e2143e6cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 특별한 교육이나 적응 기간이 필요 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d196c2f1-c869-4538-b228-71465cccccf1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-40bad554-eb11-4d04-b9ca-1fdd4e1291b2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 개발 초기를 제외하고는 특별히 시간을 할애할 이유가 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50d8643a-0b96-4179-9cee-58998173e06f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-520e7d39-70be-4fa8-92dc-ad01277dfff3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ceacb4e2-0393-4679-8cd9-ad431fde3785\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c0b47dd7-5908-4c30-9b9a-7582eea6f18a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄인 여러분 엑셀 기본 베이스의 관리용 엑셀이 필요하시다면 언제든 연락 주십시오. 물론 엑셀이 아닌 자바나 exe 파일 형태로 개발이 가능합니다. 참고해 주세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}